				<div class="text-center">
					<h1 class="hero-title text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
						AI <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-200 to-cyan-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Chat Assistant</span>
					</h1>
					<p class="hero-subtitle text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
						Automate customer support with custom-trained AI chatbots that provide 24/7 service, capture leads, and enhance your website's user experience.
